employees  by  a  registered  dental  practitioner  otherwise 
than for profit;

(c)  a  trustee  in  bankruptcy  carrying  on  through  a  registered 
dental practitioner the business of dentistry of a bankrupt 
registered dental practitioner;

(a)  has  been  convicted  in  Malaysia  or  elsewhere  of  any 
offence  punishable  with  imprisonment  (whether  in  itself 
only or in addition to or in lieu of a fine);

(b)  wilfully  and  falsely  takes  or  uses  the  name  or  title  of 
dentist, dental surgeon, qualified dentist, doctor of dental 
surgery, professor of dentistry, surgeon dentist;

(d)  and other documents issued under this Act and provide for 
